                            <comment id="14638481" author="shade" created="Tue, 9 Jan 2024 01:16:48 -0800"  >I added `21.0.3` to `Fix-Version` in &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8320871&quot; title=&quot;Release Note: Align `javac` with the Java Language Specification by Rejecting `final` in Record Patterns&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8320871&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8320871&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; release note. I believe that should be enough.</comment>
